WHITE RIVER &#8211; Police are looking for two armed suspects after Mark Hadiaris was shot dead in his home in the early hours of the morning.The incident took place on the farm of Mark McNair near White River Saw Mills.The robbers assaulted Hadiaris&#8217; wife, Sue, who was severely injured.She is being treated at Mediclinic Nelspruit.Manhunt called off after farm attackMan shot in Schagen farm attack